&lt;p&gt;To meet the demands of our high growth business, we are looking for talented Principal Consultant to drive new opportunities with our clients and lead our client engagements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What you do at Inspire11:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with clients to identify and understand business challenges helping them to craft solutions that have clearly defined top line and bottom-line impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Craft and present proposals based on identified solutions as well as write Statements of Work to execute with clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own client relationships with senior executives enabling the success of our team and the projects that we are delivering.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve our consultants as a coach and mentor through delivery and business development efforts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and oversee overall delivery quality, assessing risk, and driving overall project execution end-to-end.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guide consultants through all phases of project delivery including: requirements gathering, solution architecture, and driving an effective development team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Why you are a fit for Inspire11:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have 10+ years of consulting experience in the digital or data analytics industry&lt;/li&gt;
